These  programs  have been  published in the Finnish computer
magazines  called  C=Lehti and MikroBITTI.   All the programs
were written by Jukka and Tomi Marin.

The programs  are  freely  distributable.   You may use parts
of them in your own programs.

The programs  utilize special macros  written by the authors.
You may  request  for  the macros by  writing to the authors.
The  macros  are  copyrighted  and  may  NOT  be  used in any
commercial software or published without a written permission
of the authors.

You  may  contact the authors  by  writing  to  the following
address:

			Jukka Marin
			Ruskeisentie 24
			70900 Toivala

			FINLAND


You can also contact the authors via electronic mail:

	bitnet:		jmarin@finkuo.bitnet
